kkingen s\u00e5 var det imponerende hvor raskt ting kom p\u00e5 plass, mener han.", "Han reiste av g\u00e5rde fra Atat\u00fcrk flyplass, bare halvannen time senere enn planlagt.", "F\u00f8lg Adresseavisen p\u00e5 Facebook , Instagram og Twitter ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|utenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3430d08bb76063c0a71f7f86f80c6e6d5a7609619bca78fb8eece408d2ee4dca"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-06-29T11:03:47.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Flypassasjerer ble holdt tilbake av bev\u00e6pnede vakter utenfor flyplassen i Istanbul."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article12966631.ece/ocn2ro/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ataturk_mindre.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/43ba34031ba4fa13fbb440a7cdd46f982a51d99a.jpg?593346a6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Det var komplett kaos og vi kom ikke inn p\u00e5 flyplassomr\u00e5det -adressa.no", "- Bev\u00e6pnet politi overalt", "- Komplett kaos", "- Kom raskt p\u00e5 plass"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "43ba34031ba4fa13fbb440a7cdd46f982a51d99a"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "utenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["komplett kaos", "flyplass"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["atat\u00fcrk", "energos", "adresseavisen", "midtbudt", "hans-olav midtbust"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["tyrkia", "istanbul", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "